    "description": "Are you a skilled Digital Marketing Manager looking for your next big career move? BigBasket Consulting Pvt Ltd in Patna offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout BigBasket Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nBigBasket Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Flexible working hours\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with BigBasket Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
